dventure?\\u201D\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsxs)(n.p,{children:[\"Using the customer\\u2019s name and referencing their interests \",(0,e.jsx)(n.strong,{children:\"turns the interaction into a personal exchange\"}),\". This approach leads to higher completion rates and leaves users feeling understood, not just processed.\"]}),`\n`,(0,e.jsxs)(n.h3,{id:\"2-personalization-the-engine-of-engagement\",children:[(0,e.jsx)(n.a,{className:\"subheading-anchor\",\"aria-label\":\"Link to section\",href:\"#2-personalization-the-engine-of-engagement\",children:(0,e.jsx)(n.span,{className:\"icon icon-link\"})}),\"2. Personalization: the engine of engagement\"]}),`\n`,(0,e.jsxs)(n.p,{children:[\"Personalization drives modern \",(0,e.jsx)(n.a,{href:\"./ecommerce-chatbot\",children:\"ecommerce\"}),\". Typebot\\u2019s variable system lets you weave user responses into every step of the journey. If a customer selects \\u201C$1000-$1500\\u201D as their price range, the bot can respond, \\u201CGreat, I\\u2019ll show you the best boards in that range.\\u201D\"]}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.p,{children:\"This goes beyond repeating answers\\u2014it makes users feel recognized. For example, if Alex is interested in gift cards, the bot might say, \\u201CGift cards are a fantastic choice, Alex\\u2014especially for last-minute surprises. Would you like to see options for different occasions?\\u201D\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsxs)(n.p,{children:[\"This kind of contextual awareness, powered by variables, \",(0,e.jsx)(n.strong,{children:\"gently nudges users toward completing the quiz\"}),\".\"]}),`\n`,(0,e.jsxs)(n.h3,{id:\"3-visuals-that-guide-not-distract\",children:[(0,e.jsx)(n.a,{className:\"subheading-anchor\",\"aria-label\":\"Link to section\",href:\"#3-visuals-that-guide-not-distract\",children:(0,e.jsx)(n.span,{className:\"icon icon-link\"})}),\"3. Visuals that guide, not distract\"]}),`\n`,(0,e.jsxs)(n.p,{children:[\"A single, well-chosen image can persuade more than a block of text. When the bot presents a product recommendation, showing the product image alongside the title and price makes the suggestion more compelling. Shopify merchants have found that quizzes with product images can see up to \",(0,e.jsx)(n.strong,{children:\"30% higher click-through rates\"}),\" than those with text alone.\"]}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.p,{children:\"Visuals act as a bridge from curiosity to action. However, moderation is key. Too many images or flashy elements clutter the experience. The most effective quizzes use visuals sparingly, ensuring each image serves a clear purpose and guides the user\\u2019s attention to the next step.\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsxs)(n.h3,{id:\"4-frictionless-flow-reducing-drop-offs\",children:[(0,e.jsx)(n.a,{className:\"subheading-anchor\",\"aria-label\":\"Link to section\",href:\"#4-frictionless-flow-reducing-drop-offs\",children:(0,e.jsx)(n.span,{className:\"icon icon-link\"})}),\"4. Frictionless flow: reducing drop-offs\"]}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.p,{children:\"Every unnecessary question increases the chance users will drop off. The best product recommendation quizzes are concise, relevant, and adaptive. For example, if someone selects \\u201CAccessories,\\u201D there\\u2019s no need to ask about snowboard sizes.\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.p,{children:\"Typebot\\u2019s conditional logic lets you skip irrelevant questions, keeping the experience streamlined. Picture Priya browsing for a gift card. The bot recognizes her choice and moves straight to denomination options\\u2014no unnecessary detours.\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsxs)(n.p,{children:[\"This tailored flow respects the user\\u2019s time and reduces abandonment. Adaptive quizzes can achieve up to \",(0,e.jsx)(n.strong,{children:\"40% higher completion rates\"}),\" than static ones.\"]}),`\n`,(0,e.jsxs)(n.h3,{id:\"5-subtle-branding-and-theming\",children:[(0,e.jsx)(n.a,{className:\"subheading-anchor\",\"aria-label\":\"Link to section\",href:\"#5-subtle-branding-and-theming\",children:(0,e.jsx)(n.span,{className:\"icon icon-link\"})}),\"5. Subtle branding and theming\"]}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.p,{children:\"Branding goes beyond colors and logos\\u2014it creates an emotional connection. A quiz that uses your brand\\u2019s palette and tone feels like a natural extension of your store. For a sustainable outdoor gear shop, earth tones and conversational copy like \\u201CReady to gear up for your next adventure?\\u201D reinforce the brand\\u2019s values.\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsxs)(n.p,{children:[\"Subtlety matters. Overly aggressive branding feels forced. The best experiences gently guide users, making them feel welcome. Typebot\\u2019s theming options help you strike this balance, ensuring your quiz is both \",(0,e.jsx)(n.strong,{children:\"distinctive and inviting\"}),\".\"]}),`\n`,(0,e.jsxs)(n.h3,{id:\"6-the-power-of-micro-interactions\",children:[(0,e.jsx)(n.a,{className:\"subheading-anchor\",\"aria-label\":\"Link to section\",href:\"#6-the-power-of-micro-interactions\",children:(0,e.jsx)(n.span,{className:\"icon icon-link\"})}),\"6. The power of micro-interactions\"]}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.p,{children:\"Small touches\\u2014like a friendly emoji, a progress bar, or a personalized sign-off\\u2014can greatly improve user satisfaction. When the bot says, \\u201CThanks for sharing, Jamie! Just a sec while I find the perfect match for you\\u2026,\\u201D it mirrors the reassuring cues of a real conversation.\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsxs)(n.p,{children:[\"These micro-interactions, though easy to overlook, \",(0,e.jsx)(n.strong,{children:\"make the experience memorable\"}),\".\"]}),`\n`,(0,e.jsxs)(n.h3,{id:\"7-continuous-experimentation\",children:[(0,e.jsx)(n.a,{className:\"subheading-anchor\",\"aria-label\":\"Link to section\",href:\"#7-continuous-experimentation\",children:(0,e.jsx)(n.span,{className:\"icon icon-link\"})}),\"7. Continuous experimentation\"]}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.p,{children:\"Every audience is unique. What works for one group might not work for another. The most successful teams treat their quiz as a living experiment, adjusting question order, copy, and visuals based on real-world feedback.\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.p,{children:\"For example, changing the order of \\u201Cproduct type\\u201D and \\u201Cprice range\\u201D questions can boost completion rates. Typebot\\u2019s analytics and variable system make it easy to test and refine\\u2014so your quiz evolves with your customers.\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsxs)(n.h2,{id:\"taking-your-shopify-product-recommendations-to-the-next-level\",children:[(0,e.jsx)(n.a,{className:\"subheading-anchor\",\"aria-label\":\"Link to section\",href:\"#taking-your-shopify-product-recommendations-to-the-next-level\",children:(0,e.jsx)(n.span,{className:\"icon icon-link\"})}),\"Taking Your Shopify Product Recommendations to the Next Level\"]}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.p,{children:\"Creating a product recommendation quiz for Shopify using Typebot offers endless possibilities to enhance your customers' shopping experience.\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(n.p,{children:\"By following this tutorial as a foundation, you can customize the flow, questions, and integrations to match your unique brand voice and product catalog, ultimately driving more conversions through interactive, personalized shopping experiences.\"}),`\n`,(0,e.jsx)(o,{buttonLabel:\"Start Building\",children:\"Create, customize, and deploy your first Typebot today. No coding required.\"})]})}function g(i={}){let{wrapper:n}=i.components||{};return n?(0,e.jsx)(n,{...i,children:(0,e.jsx)(p,{...i})}):p(i)}function r(i,n){throw new Error(\"Expected \"+(n?\"component\":\"object\")+\" `\"+i+\"` to be defined: you likely forgot to import, pass, or provide it.\")}return x(q);})();\n;return Component;"